statements: SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT patient_id, scan_date, scan_result FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE eye_side = 'Left';
SELECT scan_date, eye_side, disease_progression FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE disease_progression IS NULL;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_result = 'Normal' ORDER BY scan_date DESC, patient_id
SELECT patient_id, eye_side, scan_result FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-05-31' ORDER BY patient_id
SELECT DISTINCT eye_side, COUNT(patient_id) AS total_patients FROM RetinaScanningData GROUP BY eye_side HAVING COUNT(patient_id) > 1 ORDER BY total_patients DESC
SELECT patient_id, disease_progression FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE disease_progression IS NOT NULL ORDER BY patient_id LIMIT 5
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE disease_progression LIKE '%diabetes%' OR disease_progression LIKE '%glaucoma%' AND eye_side = 'Right' ORDER BY patient_id DESC
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData
SELECT patient_id, scan_result, scan_date FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_result = 'Normal'
SELECT patient_id, scan_date FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_date > '2022-01-01'
SELECT scan_id, scan_result FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_id DESC
SELECT trend_id, patient_id, trend_date FROM EyeHealthTrends ORDER BY trend_date
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE patient_id = 100 AND scan_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT scan_id, scan_result FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-01' ORDER BY scan_id DESC;
SELECT DISTINCT patient_id, COUNT(scan_id) AS scan_count FROM RetinaScanningData GROUP BY patient_id HAVING COUNT(scan_id) > 1;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData RS INNER JOIN EyeHealthTrends EH ON RS.patient_id = EH.patient_id WHERE RS.scan_result LIKE '%normal%' AND EH.trend_analysis LIKE '%improving%';

SELECT RS.scan_id, RS.patient_id, RS.scan_date, EH.trend_date FROM RetinaScanningData RS LEFT JOIN EyeHealthTrends EH ON RS.patient_id = EH.patient_id WHERE RS.scan_result = 'abnormal' AND EH.trend_analysis LIKE '%worsening%' ORDER BY RS.scan_date ASC, EH.trend_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT scan_date, scan_data FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE patient_id = 5;
SELECT patient_id, scan_id, scan_date FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT patient_id, scan_date FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_data IS NOT NULL;
SELECT * FROM EyeHealthTrends WHERE patient_id = 10;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_date DESC, patient_id ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT patient_id, COUNT(*) AS scan_count FROM RetinaScanningData GROUP BY patient_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT * FROM EyeHealthTrends WHERE trend_description LIKE '%monitoring%' OR trend_description LIKE '%progress%';
SELECT patient_id, MAX(trend_date) AS latest_trend_date FROM EyeHealthTrends GROUP BY patient_id HAVING MAX(trend_date) IS NOT NULL;

SELECT rt.patient_id, dp.progression_date, rt.scan_date FROM RetinaScanningData rt JOIN DiseaseProgression dp ON rt.patient_id = dp.patient_id WHERE rt.scan_date < dp.progression_date ORDER BY rt.scan_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData;
SELECT patient_id, scan_date, scan_result FROM RetinaScanningData ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT disease_id, disease_name FROM DiseaseProgression WHERE progression_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT patient_id, history_date, health_status FROM HealthHistory WHERE patient_id = 101 AND history_date = '2022-05-15';
SELECT trend_description, trend_value FROM EyeHealthTrends WHERE trend_value > 50 ORDER BY trend_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE patient_id = 100 ORDER BY scan_date DESC;
SELECT scan_result FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2021-12-31' ORDER BY patient_id ASC, scan_date ASC;
SELECT patient_id, scan_result FROM RetinaScanningData WHERE scan_result LIKE '%healthy%' AND patient_id IN (200, 201, 202);
SELECT disease_name, progression_date FROM DiseaseProgression WHERE progression_date < '2022-01-01' ORDER BY progression_date DESC;
SELECT patient_id, health_status FROM HealthHistory WHERE history_date = '2022-05-15' AND patient_id > 150 ORDER BY patient_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningResults;
SELECT patient_id, scan_date, scan_result FROM RetinaScanningResults WHERE patient_id = 1;
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM PatientInformation WHERE age > 50 ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT disease_name, stage FROM DiseaseProgression WHERE stage < 3;
SELECT trend_name, observation_date, observation_value FROM HealthTrends WHERE observation_value > 100 ORDER BY observation_date;
SELECT * FROM RetinaScanningResults ORDER BY scan_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT patient_name, age, gender FROM PatientInformation WHERE gender='Male';
SELECT disease_name, stage, diagnosis_date FROM DiseaseProgression WHERE stage > 2;
SELECT trend_name, observation_value FROM HealthTrends WHERE observation_value < 50.0 ORDER BY observation_date ASC;
SELECT record_id, health_condition FROM EyeHealthRecords WHERE patient_id = 1001;
